name: Cat People
overview: Cat people come in all shapes and sizes, but they share a love for their enchanting, unique feline friends. This docuseries reveals their tales.

episodes.name: Cat Rappers Delight
episodes.overview: Baths get a bad rap with felines. Yet after a video of rapper Moshow freestyling and washing kitty DJ Ravioli goes viral, this cat family cleans up.

episodes.name: The Cat Show Must Go On
episodes.overview: Training cats can look like a three-ring circus. But Samantha embraces the challenge as her performing pusses dazzle onstage. Then adversity strikes.

episodes.name: Copycat
episodes.overview: How do you truly capture a cat? Inspired by her three rescues, Sachi of Wakuneco relies on needle felting to create heartfelt, lifelike 3D portraits.

episodes.name: Paws For The Cause
episodes.overview: A renowned "chonker" gives back: Mr. B's Random Acts of Kindness raises cash for cats in need, inspired by "TrapKing" Sterling's spay-neuter nonprofit.

episodes.name: God's Little People
episodes.overview: A frail feral kitten spurs a couple's move to the Greek island of Syros to start a sanctuary for stray felines, where they save lives and find homes.
